{"tid":1835623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2003年4月9號沙士嘅死亡率係2.8%，而家新型冠狀病毒係2.98%","createTime":"2020-01-23T02:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T02:26:31.000Z","uid":115205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db54ac79ad56adb7030f682e7f3e5339c84cfe32","tid":1835623,"uid":115205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:08:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2003年</span></strong>：<br />\nThe SARS case fatality rate in Hong Kong increased from <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.2 percent</span></strong> (17/761 &times; 100) on April 4, 2003, to 17.0 percent (299/1,755 &times; 100) by September 22, 2003. <br />\n<a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/aje/article/159/3/229/79939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Faje%2Farticle%2F159%2F3%2F229%2F79939&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9351091a\" target=\"_blank\">https://academic.oup.com/aje/article/159/3/229/79939</a><br />\n<br />\nThe actual case fatality ratio in Hong Kong as of April 9, 2003 was <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.8%</span></strong> (27 deaths of 970 confirmed cases) <a href=\"https://jech.bmj.com/content/57/11/857#ref-12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjech.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F57%2F11%2F857%23ref-12&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=fda3969d\" target=\"_blank\">https://jech.bmj.com/content/57/11/857#ref-12</a><br />\n<br />\n最後沙士係香港死亡率係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>17％</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年</span></strong>1月22號2400：<br />\n571例17死 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(2.98%)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家出街帶番個罩，千祈唔好鬆懈。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc125d47fc5b2de62af7dae25c02f2093e58d6f","tid":1835623,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>有冇人有興趣揾日一齊去飲啖茶食下姜</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊係坐爆成間舖頭，坐晚市三個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入嚟推post啦</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1833914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1833914</a><br />\n<br />\n可以留意下呢個Telegram頻道<br />\n希望大家集思廣益，打經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</div>"}]}